<br>
I am now Semi-Retired after 3 years of dedicated playing.  No longer is EQ the focus of my gaming fun.  I hope to retire compltly in a month.  <br>
<br>
Reasons:<br>
<br>
1.  Too hard to find exp groups guilded or not.<br>
